    "name": "Planetary Delivery Boys",
    "steam_appid": 3314270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/729d3af433f1b0095427a779dd5ac0b4.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1560 height=232 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The <strong>Planetary Delivery Boys</strong> is a 1-4 player co-op horror experience. Your mission: Escort high-value cargo across a hostile galaxy aboard the automated Company Train.  <br><br>Keep the engine running by managing power, monitoring the CCTV system and sealing manual security doors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/e7269bb149d850ff080b9391a7871df5.poster.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1170 height=329 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/e7269bb149d850ff080b9391a7871df5.webm?t=1769416945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/38de630041b3f4009514c9052b6c1506.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1560 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Success requires teamwork, but survival requires cold statistics. To reach the destination safely, an <strong>IDS ASSET</strong> must be ready to make the ultimate sacrifice. If power production stalls, do not hesitate to turn your <strong>colleagues into fuel</strong> to keep the train moving!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/24760e02aa8f44fffea24a72b118319f.poster.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/24760e02aa8f44fffea24a72b118319f.webm?t=1769416945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/86e1026311daaec0318d0b16958136e0.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1560 height=232 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">As an <strong>IDS ASSET</strong> your journey may be difficult. The company has provided the following recommendations:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Station</strong>: Invite friends, select destinations, spend credits on upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Transi</strong>t: Defend cargo, maintain shared power, decide who is expendable  <br><strong>The Ultimate Rule</strong>: Keep packages safe<u>,</u> <u>at all costs.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/43f980cab38cbc566974bcfc6f5a0f14.poster.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1170 height=329 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/43f980cab38cbc566974bcfc6f5a0f14.webm?t=1769416945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/fbb5973ae6d7f93fa0f307b2a7a3bb6b.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1560 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Maintaining the wagons is only half the battle; you must also survive the transit. Keep your equipment running, and be careful of what lurks in the vents...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/cb8a4e68aaf835a3581be9a4973f8137.poster.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/cb8a4e68aaf835a3581be9a4973f8137.webm?t=1769416945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/10cdc78d0cf7897d476b16783d48ac6d.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1560 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The company has provided the <strong>CCTV System</strong>. Utilize this effectively to scout for evil-doers, while managing your power across the entire train. Every door you close and light you flick drains the train. Once power hits zero, <strong>all systems go dark</strong>, and every security door on the train slides open. You don't want to be inside when that happens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/fa64d577e144db8401f974266d8d656b.poster.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/fa64d577e144db8401f974266d8d656b.webm?t=1769416945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/ce10a1336b8fe2669e984ba313c2bee7.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1560 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Every employee is issued a standard duty <strong>Multi-Tool </strong>for long range communication and fending off thieves. Your tools require juice, you can charge your<strong> Personal Battery </strong>by draining the train's power. Every charge you take for yourself, is a charge taken away from the train's defence systems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/a8d2b429eba21de52f223fc0ab3dbcf0.poster.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/a8d2b429eba21de52f223fc0ab3dbcf0.webm?t=1769416945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314270/extras/a5f1511cb4cff3f42805d9db28b700e3.avif?t=1769416945\" width=1560 height=232 /></span>The<strong> Planetary Delivery Boys</strong> is currently still in development. Follow along for more details!</p>",
